{"tid":29880,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"陳七：韋拿踢法似我","createTime":"2016-12-09T00:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T08:52:24.000Z","uid":20933,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"13efd2953492cb673c0faa8d60941405613278f9","tid":29880,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T00:38:34.000Z","msg":"最近榮膺美職（MLS）最有價值球員的紐約城前鋒韋拿將於明日訪港，南華前鋒陳肇麒曾自比韋拿一事再被熱炒，不過陳七就未有對事件再作回應。<br />\n<br />\n陳肇麒於2010年一次訪問中，比較西班牙的韋拿和德國高路斯射術時對記者說了一句「韋拿踢法似我」，被網民認為他大言不慚，並因此而被稱為「陳韋拿」、「Villa Chan」等。陳七於2014年另一個訪問中否認說過有關說話，但為免又被人指責故叮囑記者不要澄清，而記者細查後亦發現原來報導也沒直接引述陳七說「踢法似我」。及後，陳七有向傳媒解釋，指當年是想說自己踢法有點似韋拿但就口快說錯了韋拿踢法似自己，結果被外界放大，並謂怎可能說韋拿踢法似自己。"},{"pid":"12505a53da976b2ac60213c8bd04d1af2df1bea5","tid":29880,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T00:40:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56021872&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161208\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56021872%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161208&d=cHB5jyzH%2BO0d22hICkGRnksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=03228c16\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56021872%26category_guid%3D7032049%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20161208&h=34bd46a8\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56021872&amp;category_guid=7032049&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20161208</a>"},{"pid":"c25de47c1d4c483afa5afb4cefab49a5b8a2f353","tid":29880,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T00:47:02.000Z","msg":"而家陳韋拿去左邊"},{"pid":"e30156bf2c1cbcaaab119237fb564a3cb25ea0ae","tid":29880,"uid":2438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T00:52:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> binc"},{"pid":"8c5d0cc523e61c3550f4fd75b18b3bb8eb949c17","tid":29880,"uid":20933,"like